  {
    "uuid": "27ea98c4-7916-5bd2-81c6-bb5fdc0aa6c9",
    "entry": "刃長",
    "reading": {
      "primary": "はちょう",
      "alternatives": [],
      "is_heteronym": false
    },
    "grammar": {
      "pos": [
        "名詞"
      ],
      "ctype": null,
      "inflections": null
    },
    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "length of a blade",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [],
          "literary": [
            {
              "text": "今一刃ヲ加フ、但シ刃長ケレバ則チ棒頭力無シ、他ノ棒ヲ圧スルコト能ハズ、只二寸ヲ可トス、形｜鴨嘴ノ如シ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "大菩薩峠",
                "author": "新月の巻",
                "note": "青空文庫"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "この店はちょうど自分が今の処に移る少し前に新しく出来たそうである。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "やもり物語",
